    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black, a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-compression power plant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver 333hp with an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable Differential Lock. Mechanically, the car is well-sorted: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal timing advance. The suspension maintains its factory geometry, offering the precise turn-in and lateral stability the E46 chassis is celebrated for. While the exterior and interior show minor patina consistent with a well-enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical vitals\u2014including recent valve clearances and rod bearing inspections\u2014confirm its readiness for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
