    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between a daily driver and a weekend enthusiast car. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor rock chips on the front fascia and a small, shallow scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats show light bolster wear but remain supple and free of any punctures or tears. All instrumentation, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. I have kept a comprehensive folder of service records, including a recent oil change, brake pad replacement, and a fresh set of performance all-season tires with less than 2,000 miles on them. The engine pulls smoothly through the rev range, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. This is a turn-key example for someone who values mechanical integrity and a well-cared-for aesthetic.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in commendable condition, this vehicle exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and refined aesthetics. Meticulously maintained and subjected to rigorous inspection, it offers a driving experience characterized by mechanical precision and interior comfort. This represents a premier opportunity for the sophisticated buyer seeking a reliable, high-caliber vehicle that commands a distinguished presence on the road. We invite you to experience the enduring quality and exceptional value inherent in this well-appointed example.",
