    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend adventure, this car is ready to hit the road with you! It\u2019s been well-loved, runs great, and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to help you get behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
